## Create an item

### Request Body

```json
{
  "Name": "Rock Fountain",
  "IncomeAccountRef": {
    "value": "79"
  },
  "ExpenseAccountRef": {
    "value": "80"
  },
  "AssetAccountRef": {
    "value": "81"
  },
  "Type": "Inventory",
  "TrackQtyOnHand": true,
  "QtyOnHand": 10,
  "InvStartDate": "2023-04-01"
}
```

## Query an item

### Request

```
GET /v3/company/<realmId>/query?query=select * from Item where Name = 'Rock Fountain'
```

## Read an item

### Request

```
GET /v3/company/<realmId>/item/<id>
```

